    00 (0)           0           No
    01 (1)           1           1st
    02 (10)          3           1st -> 2nd -> 1st
    03 (11)          2           2nd -> 1st
    04 (100)         7           1st -> 2nd -> 1st -> 2nd -> 1st -> 2nd -> 1st
